    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Zombies!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to Kismet, the post-apocalyptic zombie shooter where your only options are to gear up or die. (Scary pixel creatures warning!)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3329150/extras/9b6e976c6c66a85e023de190f2fda077.avif?t=1750618383\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3329150/extras_big/9b6e976c6c66a85e023de190f2fda077.avif?t=1750618383 width=800 height=267 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Explore unique maps</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Uncover twisted experiments in Tapor, roam an isolated farm in Fjord, or explore an abandoned spacecraft in Prairie. Kismet offers three distinct maps on launch each with their own twists. Find and build powerful weapons to aid your survival against hordes of the undead and... aliens?(!)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3329150/extras/a5d84ef675c7bcc6196fa27f60e49cf6.avif?t=1750618383\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3329150/extras_big/a5d84ef675c7bcc6196fa27f60e49cf6.avif?t=1750618383 width=800 height=267 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Build your defenses</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fighting hordes of mutilated enemies can be tough with just a gun, so build turrets and traps to help! Repair generators to open new areas of maps or fix up the med-bay for strong buffs. But be careful! Enemies can still destroy these systems so it's important to defend these areas appropriately.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3329150/extras/d43131bdc4930ff0e0a52981f57511ae.avif?t=1750618383\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3329150/extras_big/d43131bdc4930ff0e0a52981f57511ae.avif?t=1750618383 width=800 height=267 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Additional Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customizable characters</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A quirky robot computer</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Secret boss fight</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >HD PIXEL GRAPHICS</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Caps lock</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I think there might be a cat somewhere? I forget.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Niche references no one will understand</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Raspberry</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
